title: Dak Cheung district
content:
Dak Cheung is a district (muang) of Sekong province in southeastern Laos.[1]

The District Governor of Dak Cheung District (2017) is Mr. Laysouane Midsouvanh (ໄລສວນ ມິດສຸວັນ).[citation needed]
